CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 22, 1958, pg. 22, reads: "Novice Champs - Three champions in Senior Novice Division of the Golden Gloves are, from left to right: Featherweight Leroy Gray, Lee Moore A. C.; lightweight Bill Rebholz, Brasher Association, and welterweight Carl Daniels, Glen Hazel Boys Club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Golden Gloves Senior Novice Division boxing champions, including from left: featherweight Leroy Gray, lightweight Bill Rebholz, welterweight Carl Daniels, and three others wearing satin robes and posed with left fists raised, in Pitt Field House, University of Pittsburgh
